txt.en: Urshúlagar can be found in Emyn Duir.\n\nYou should destroy tents at Urshúlagar.

At the command of Sauron, Easterlings and Black Númenóreans keep watch over the pass to Emyn Duir, the Shadowfells, gathering at Urshúlagar to make their plans. Destroying what you can of the encampment should hinder any schemes they seek to unleash upon the Great Alliance.
Urshúlagar can be found in Emyn Duir.\n\nYou should destroy tents at Urshúlagar.
You destroyed many tents at the encampment of Urshúlagar. Surely the evil Men who gather there will be hindered by your efforts, their plans put to smoke.
Many evil Men gather at the encampment of Urshúlagar, prepared to do the bidding of Sauron.
